<text>[[Farnham]] is a town in Surrey, England, within the Borough of Waverley.

Farnham may also refer to:

== Places ==
=== Canada ===
* Farnham, Quebec

=== United Kingdom ===
* Farnham, Dorset
* Farnham, Essex
* Farnham, Northumberland, now in Hepple
* Farnham, North Yorkshire
* Farnham, Suffolk
* Farnham, Surrey
** Farnham Castle, Surrey
* Farnham Common, Buckinghamshire
* Farnham Royal, Buckinghamshire

=== United States ===
* Farnham, New York
* Farnham, Virginia
* Farnham Creek, a stream in Minnesota
* Farnham Lake, a lake in Minnesota

== People ==
*Farnham (surname)

== Fiction ==
* Farnham the Drunk, a character in the popular role playing game &quot;Diablo&quot;
