== Selected radio ==
Timothy West was a member of the BBC Radio Drama Repertory Company in 1962 and took part in over 500 radio broadcasts. In 1959, he wrote and produced a short audio play, &quot;This Gun That I Have in My Right Hand Is Loaded&quot;, satirising typical mistakes of radio drama, including over-explanatory dialogue and misuse of sound cues.

